{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/steam_description_01-2.gif?t=1735922701\" /><br><br>Behind the Frame is a vivid, interactive fiction about an aspiring artist on the cusp of finishing the final piece of her gallery submission.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/steam_description_02-2.gif?t=1735922701\" /><br><br>A relaxing, eloquent experience that can be played at any pace. Become immersed in a panoramic world filled with resplendent colors, beautiful hand-animated visuals, and a smooth, easy-listening soundtrack. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/steam_description_03-2.gif?t=1735922701\" /><br><br>As a passionate artist, seek the missing colors that will bring your paintings to life - all while remembering to take the occasional coffee and breakfast breaks that keep you going. There is more than what meets the eye, for every painting has a story to tell.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1634150/extras/steam_description_04-2.gif?t=1735922701\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Inspiration","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1634150/d122b91ed4bc7360cb4280f07c915629e830c268.jpg"},{"name":"Turning Point","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1634150/1c8f23726d027206ab228f5c04c36a00bb2d83b1.jpg"},{"name":"Encounter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1634150/12fdf182e58f85289f78874b43e0f61fdb145929.jpg"},{"name":"Behind the Frame","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1634150/4ed0e192952009a885b933f3cf33b09b952634b8.jpg"},{"name":"You've Pressed 78 Buttons","path":"https://cd